{"tid":114514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"須自行蒐證　律政司可申終止","createTime":"2017-02-09T23:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T02:24:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b113e0ff5d6334480d16857753d643fd251b4e88","tid":114514,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T23:56:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19923856&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19923856%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170210&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=300cca0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19923856%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170210&h=95df13d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19923856&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170210</a><br />\n<br />\n須自行蒐證　律政司可申終止<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n■受害人的法律團隊昨向律政司司長袁國強發公開信。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n<br />\n根據《裁判官條例》第14條，任何人都可向裁判法院申請私人檢控，如果裁判官接納，會向被告發出傳票。<br />\n<br />\n有法律界人士指，若律政司及警方對某些刑事案件不作檢控，相關受害人可循私人檢控途徑追究，<span style=\"color: red;\">但申請者需自行調查舉證，須提供足夠證據，裁判官才會接納其案件；蒐證工作由原告人及代表律師「一手包辦」，耗費龐大人力物力，「要包辦搵證據、證人，但又冇執法者嘅調查、拘捕權力，過程好困難」。</span><br />\n<br />\n該法律界人士又指，審訊過程中，律政司可介入，成為檢控的一方，若律政司認為有人濫用私人檢控權利，更可申請終止檢控。<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;now員工私人檢控警方無進展<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;感冒出事中原好上司急求肝　手足呼籲好心人施援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味， 有需要一定捐錢支持，<br />\n希望睇到既人都出嚟做證人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0212a3acb3e4184b42ef9092df36663e30f121e3","tid":114514,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:00:14.000Z","msg":"算唔算助訟？"},{"pid":"05be5d24e0ec758b73873323504575db47451c90","tid":114514,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:06:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算唔算助訟？</blockquote><br />\n應該唔算， 刑事罪行兼我無任何金錢得益。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffbf2f1523b0ebc8d292defccceee0b8e542285","tid":114514,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>算唔算助訟？</blockquote><br />\n應該唔算， 刑事罪行兼我無任何金錢得益。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n贏/輸 我都無金錢利益<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2d486632881943b97056cc20e4f5bea9b20ac6","tid":114514,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:20:56.000Z","msg":"講緊柒警案？"},{"pid":"98e773a5c6e582840a724cf57fd093df069886a0","tid":114514,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講緊柒警案？</blockquote><br />\n朱經緯"},{"pid":"af19916bd796fe3d0678ccfced9b095d19fa0310","tid":114514,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:50:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講緊柒警案？</blockquote><br />\n朱經緯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170210/280pix/a0101a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170210%2F280pix%2Fa0101a.gif&h=9d9784ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■2014年11月底，警司朱經緯於旺角涉以警棍毆打鄭仲恒。"},{"pid":"f4087dc2c8d975ba9391b1ebc7a1078ca2112432","tid":114514,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T00:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cla